<!-- -*- mode: sgml -*-

     XML Document Type Definition for polarities extracted from a tree
     adjoining grammar.

     Copyright (C) 2008 INRIA
     Author: Sylvain Schmitz <Sylvain.Schmitz@loria.fr>

     TODO: copy licence here.
